column5: Took a buddies son out today, wind was strong and the waves were coming from the NW with some 4 footers, so we headed into Baie Du Dore to fish for Pike or Bass we thought and this is what we got, Josh wanted to take it home so we did, it might be getting BBQ'd as we speak Richard
He must have thought he had a monster bass or pike . Definitly a good side-catch.!
Congrats to Josh on that beauty Thanks for sharing Richard!!! Leechman
